title: Does Anybody Still Race 10/10ths These Days? - /SHAKEDOWN
description: Max Seeger of FastLaneDaily and /DRIVE asks Leo Parente of ShakeDown who asks you-If driving 10/10th is still part of racing these days. Typically, SD brings you evidence and examples, asks your opinion, then seeks your nominations for racers that best embody 10/10th racing. From any generation, any racing discipline.
